      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m confused about inputRect and its relationship to src in reverse mode.  So |src| is in local coordinates and |inputRect| is some super-clip, always in device space?  Can you comment on why it\u0027s ok to ignore/pass nullptr here?",
      "range": {
